@startuml
title State Diagram: Work Package Workflow

(*) --> "New"

' New State
"New" --> "Analyze"
"New" --> "Blocked"
"New" --> "Done"
    note on link
        in case work package
        is obsolete
    end note

' Analyze State
"Analyze" --> "In Progress"
"Analyze" --> "Blocked"
"Analyze" --> "Done"

' In Progress State
"In Progress" --> "Analyze"
    note on link
        in case new
        information forces
        the work package
        to be re-evaluated
    end note
"In Progress" --> "Blocked"
"In Progress" --> "Done"

' Blocked State
"Blocked" --> "Analyze"
"Blocked" --> "In Progress"

' Done State
"Done" --> "Analyze"
"Done" --> (*)

@enduml
